    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini Dei Salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Concessimus nos <rs
                            key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">vir gloriosissimus</rs> domnus
                            <persName ref="#people/2004" key="#Marquis/duke">Romovald</persName>
                        summus <rs key="#Marquis/duke">dux</rs> gentis Langubardorum in <orgName
                            key="#Churches #Private_foundations" ref="#juridical_persons/3401"><rs
                                key="#Churches #Private_foundations">ęcclesia</rs> Beate Sancte
                            Sophie</orgName> quam <persName ref="#people/3453" key="#Abbots"
                            >Zacharia</persName> venerabilis <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> a
                        fundamentis edificavit, hoc est <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Aqueducts #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            >de aqueducto publico fistolam aque</rs> quem erga <rs key="#Walls"
                            >muro</rs> huius felicissime civitatis nostre instruere visus est et
                        usque ad prephatam ęcclesiam comportavit, ut perhennis temporibus ipsa
                        fistola in ipsa ęcclesia sine detentium currat et prephate ęcclesię <rs
                            key="#Priests">sacerdotes</rs> sibi eam privatam defendati, et nullus
                        habeat licentiam exinde sine voluntate de sacerdote eius inplere aut ibi
                        facere invasionem, nisi qui ab eiusdem locis <rs key="#Slave"
                            >servientibus</rs> permissus fuerit, nęque a nostri sacri palatii
                        iudicem aliquando subtrahatur; simul etiam et concessimus in nostrum
                        venerabilem locum <rs
                            key="#Gualdi #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >vvaldum</rs> nostrum de <rs key="#Rivers">fluvio</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Rivers #Gualdi #Fiscal_property" ref="#places/2315"
                            >Calore</placeName>, hoc est <rs key="#Fines">fine</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/3461" key="#Gualdi #Fiscal_property">vado
                            carrario</placeName>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/3438"> Sancti
                            Marciani</orgName> et usque sub casa Valeri, ut a nunc et semper homines
                        de ipsa ecclesia <rs key="#Fisheries">piscationem</rs> faciant, et nullus
                        sine permissum sacerdotis nominate ęcclesię in ipso vvaldo habeat licentiam
                        introire ad piscendum, sed sicuti actenus ad nostra manum defensus est, ita
                        et a sepe phata ecclesia defendatur, et a nullum quemquam hominem nunquam ab
                        ipsum venerabilem locum aliquando subtrahatur, sed perpetuis temporibus iure
                        ab ante lata ęcclesia et a Zacharia abbate vel ab eius ordinati sacerdotibus
                        deteneatur. Quod vero preceptum concessionis ex iussione nostre potestati
                        dictavi ego <persName key="#Other_palatine_officer" ref="#people/3481"
                            >Audelahis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer">vicedominus et referendario</rs> tibi
                            <persName ref="#people/3482" key="#Notary">Aldichis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scribendum. Actum <placeName key="#Cities"
                            ref="#places/110">Benevento</placeName> in palatio mense decembrio per
                        indictione decima Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
